channel.title: Forumite Pictures and other Community galleries
channel.description:
Yes, this is the new "post your picture" thread, but it is much more than that. This is the introduction to the new picture galleries!
I found a much easier way to maintain picture galleries rather than using my own webserver/space which in the end became horribly tedious to update. I am sure some of you will pshaw at Picasa web albums, but it cuts down the time it takes to upload updates by 90% and I am happy with the way it works.
So with that said, feel free to take a look at the new galleries found here and remember to continue posting your pictures!
[FONT='Arial Narrow'][url='https://picasaweb.google.com/blackmesasource.com']Black Mesa Source.com's Public Gallery[/url][/SIZE][/FONT] Found here are: Pictures of our forum members Black Mesa Covers Box Art Vending Machine Candy Xen Concept Art Advertise Black Mesa
